<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/43000603/2025-26/evaluation> a ns1:EvaluationSystem ;
    ns1:evaluationDescription """Note

This subject involves mandatory practical activities that must be taken during the schol period as tehy require dedicated means that are only available at that time. If they are not taken during the school period, the maximum
grade in the global evaluation cannot be achieved.
Non-attendance to practical sessions and visits will be penalized with 2% of the final mark
The total pass mark is 5/10.
Progressive assessment:
Computer simulations delivery. (17.5 % final mark), pass mark (4/10)
Attendance to practical sessio and visits. Compulsory and not recoverable (12,5% final mark)
Optical microscope & Profilometry delivery (1,5% final mark), pass mark (4/10)
Scanning Tunnelling Microscopy delivery (2,0% final mark), pass mark (4/10)
Atomic Force Microscopy delivery (2,5% final mark), pass mark (4/10)
XRD delivery (4% final mark), pass mark (4/10)
Written exam (60%final mark), pass mark (4/10)
Second opportunity exam
The total pass mark is 5/10.
Deliverys (27.5 % final mark), pass mark (4/10)
Written exam (60 % final mark), pass mark (4/10)"""@es ;
